junit.framework.Test
public class EPPPersRegTst
extends junit.framework.TestCase

Is a unit test of the com.verisign.epp.codec.persreg package. The unit test will execute, gather statistics, and output the results of a test of each com.verisign.epp.codec.persreg package concrete extension EPPCodecComponent's. The Domain and Email Forwarding commands and responses are used to test extending both.

The unit test is dependent on the use of JUNIT 3.5
